{"h5740eed4g4047g4a41ga797g2b6ddfe2746e": ["Go on. If he doesn't wake... I'll find you.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "d69eb441-359f-e549-eea9-7eb4ebaa8d5f"], "heaf1d581gad8bg4c05gb5f9g673e7d74cfb3": ["Leave us alone.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "1ed1e069-17f3-ec96-812e-30a79c95e8ec"], "h635ae53dge732g4c35g913dg39b6be3317d3": ["Please, let him rest.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "8979e19f-b847-0e49-b6ef-0abb8caf8e10"], "hdcb5b672gafeeg4accg8693gd6626402d511": ["Stay back!", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "93890b81-ac31-5a00-252d-1329e1c98958"], "hc64d1c9dgeb56g4f8agaaabg29d42a7ae7f9": ["Keep moving, stranger. <i>Quietly</i>.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "3cf89180-fde3-13a1-2261-a5521e9fde11"], "hdfab90b7geffbg497bg9ad0gc59792a77a17": ["What happened here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "5c64cd5b-57c3-387e-2f9e-0e318a92ab72"], "h99bf953eg00c8g4bd3g94aeg4d72a81b989e": ["I told you to go!", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "470b8c84-fb18-e903-6b8c-24ebd4ac6277"], "h0927e8c4gd4e5g4cedg9979gae0bfa1fd28f": ["You're Scratch, aren't you? Come here. It's all right.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "a084a47b-9660-c953-e99d-c6371c8588cc"], "ha14afedbge61fg4d83ga625g34a429ecd85a": ["You know my name? Interesting - a predator wouldn't care to learn it.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "861f5a48-ba61-9194-c1ff-298c4408d761"], "hb7035edfg0761g41d3ga80bg666e6802ba1d": ["<i>Peer at his collar.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "fae6e3cb-a88d-0ab1-4ea8-5fe2205de458"], "h0c51a565ga939g450fg9587gdfdbbf6aafd9": ["*You see a name etched into the leather - 'Scratch'.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "411e1a84-3754-a5ac-c8ff-ccaa0e1237d1"], "h0c309845g1321g4c27gae58gf59767f8f9d9": ["What are you doing? Get back!", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "1c305154-b2b1-e3bc-7d46-13735346e5d5"], "haeac55a5g6031g481cg9f89g66a23583f8de": ["If I wanted to hurt either of you, I'd have done it already.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "daa36c00-2e45-6bd1-9c18-cdaa2a43f106"], "h7811d9a9gae1fg477egb1b2gf731ccbb909e": ["Perhaps that's true. Your scent is thick with blood.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "4566ac82-0111-237d-ed66-9e01c606a2b7"], "hca6c93bega20ag4ff6g90c5g3fe1f807e5c4": ["Still, you should go. My friend is injured. He needs rest.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "3b57aac0-9f24-e550-273f-e56427ab6f7d"], "h10a2aa8ag83ceg42d2ga8e1gffc77a8eb026": ["I don't think he's going to wake up.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "213cbfd7-bfa3-1599-fb13-ac8bded80955"], "hc01c86ebg0d1cg4e8fgac00g15fcc48d5db7": ["Of course he will. And then we'll return home.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "97d762da-bd30-f6bd-fc3f-86b0a32ecc0c"], "h63ac169ag84d2g4994g8899gb1c7c35f66e3": ["What's your name?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "f6106178-9fb3-e5a8-e1e0-d00c7cbdd2d5"], "h248afc6ag2247g4991g9359g310ee673835b": ["He calls me Scratch. You can do the same.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "c936a64e-95ed-2ed3-9958-55a4fc9921e2"], "h26081b40gd15eg4093g8a2ag43a9f15d71aa": ["What happened to your friend, exactly?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "508ceb00-d61a-ce81-54fb-769882063cf4"], "h28ac6cdagdfb2g45aag9e7bg365fc92e60a6": ["We were attacked. Cackling, furry things on two legs.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "e6a7b91c-2424-0e23-4c15-367a8f2bc7a9"], "ha5b775e2gafc2g40d7g8394g41ef32d8e9cc": ["And their smell... it was strange. Rotten. <i>Evil</i>.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "aa70c9f6-a758-4a71-6146-701f716512b8"], "hdcda33f8g9648g4d17g8756g2f63ee564501": ["*You know the creatures he describes - gnolls.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "6f52e9d2-6d71-58ac-fa00-92741a0382da"], "h6621665ag71c7g40c5ga211g79c84c7b4180": ["Come on, you can travel with me if you like.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "b895307f-57dd-6f81-9e2c-bb26d58842b7"], "h024f1147g5373g44a8gbff7g5e32779d87e8": ["No. I won't leave him.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "4c5c33b1-ec3d-78f9-a704-a129316ff5b7"], "h2f0e5c2agdf4cg4fbdg92f2g575f05ac80c1": ["If he doesn't wake up, follow my scent. I have a camp.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "abfd6250-2902-c6ab-257a-cac3fcbd4c75"], "h00ab1f39g4916g4803ga73fg61e6a058489e": ["If it comes to that... I may. Thank you.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "c6a9fe94-f672-f06b-9774-b629923a4517"], "h7c6d0281gd395g4a6egbf82gc723813ed600": ["<i>Prove the man is dead - shout at his corpse.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "edf0e4a7-9f4f-6225-1d69-6c4f45b01dbb"], "hb6a59b79g12f5g4324gadafg05fd73d1b81b": ["That's enough!", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "23ff891d-a1ba-fc79-28f8-405e7175359f"], "hd46a31e0gc9a6g4402g97abgd1166d818839": ["Rest? He needs a grave.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "f06e4e58-842f-e734-0754-3552cb859c05"], "h8972e0ecg3600g4e80g915cg404d407527bf": ["Just go. I won't ask you again.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "20d9b8db-67db-8317-45fb-21cadbc09dbb"], "ha2e151b8g744ag4babgb3f6g578a6b9476d4": ["It's noble to protect one of your clan, but he's gone.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "4c6fff3d-862f-a0e0-e9bc-b36cc68a1e7f"], "h1857d8eegd27dg40cag8cb1gdcd922c30722": ["He's not my clan. He's my <i>friend</i>.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "7be6fa5b-6761-d402-a626-02933b86287e"], "h69546f28gc0e6g4098g9870g86c7db547cb2": ["Stop deluding yourself - you are guarding a corpse.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "bf61779f-774f-e6b9-1e46-a1fb71dc87e5"], "h5e31f0fag8e52g4240g9acbgef4b6549bf44": ["Your words are uglier than the rest of you.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "431d9e93-2d88-fb84-a34a-dfa652350fdb"], "h42e35871g469dg46e0g9845gb27d5cf13d58": ["Go back to whatever hole you slithered out of.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "60d755b1-cd67-8901-ca7a-c33c8158bd47"], "h492c1c9bgf6c8g4456gb4e3g42e29d1b9a50": ["He's with his god now. I'm sorry.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "43e83e21-3ae8-f42d-919b-5ee121de1f3f"], "h78cd2dc3g0f03g4a97gac1cg2882295f3aad": ["It's not over yet. He'll wake up.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "3ad39f51-02e3-9589-302b-600e71519521"], "hb351d841gd04ag424dg8132g75d09e04ed19": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "b10382b0-3f89-678c-7a35-779bc46e36fc"], "h3fedac6eg4000g43faga55ag64e2d8960ad2": ["You snarl, but you have no teeth. ", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "5f6550a2-b579-17c3-acc4-51580214eef8"], "h237597a3gbd22g4238ga218gf25928d0403c": ["I could snap you in half, <i>if</i> I wanted to. I don't.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "efbd1908-275e-44b1-4688-4ab5dd2c56f6"], "h38606731g2128g4172g9480geef16629f458": ["I'm not an enemy, I promise.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "79c7e66c-9d60-5372-9fc9-c6891aa7c412"], "h4c7e210cg9473g4e69g9bbagab733fb1e656": ["Hm. There's death in your scent, but not in your words.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "705e76f3-a95b-7bd2-28e7-817a43a39512"], "h63f9cc88ge3f2g413bgbd2eg7db646d9db00": ["These wilds crawl with monsters. You could be one of them.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "13057e9c-a4b7-70e8-0ec4-77fa7b699998"], "hac0e837cge37bg4dd0gb4e7g2e4d038560d5": ["Calm, friend. I mean you no harm.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "91310d4c-ded4-3d28-a029-7df10e065435"], "h8bd14f2age323g4953gaf1fg4e1d1f607cd9": ["I understand your fear, but I promise I mean you no harm.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "e2dd45dd-1b2c-b517-50eb-22ddf5062bed"], "hea775f66gef90g46e3g932cg0d3a03ab9dcc": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "16a84772-80ac-56d5-d99d-72b00c688d89"], "h25b15b46ge283g43a1g80a0g31cec405c8e3": ["Who is that?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "3e09bffb-68d4-8bcb-4d6d-d19926cf0d34"], "h8ce9c623g3820g4de0gab9fge3f61788470c": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "32a62b44-7110-b976-d32e-6143693a2bd5"], "h3ba57f40g898fg4737g83aeg1b3824baa9a7": ["*The dog remains at the dead man's side, as if in mourning.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "529309fc-830a-99f9-a5b9-e880cfdb7f56"], "h07fe9960g7680g4818gb778gf3dd5be064e2": ["*The dog flashes its teeth in a snarl - he wants you gone.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "2a16be4e-8bd5-afd0-b6d5-ff9c1b996be4"], "ha8f1d514g24afg48c4g8b09g5e71d9f4a733": ["*Grrr!*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "2baa694d-ffbd-f65d-61ff-ae5be60af473"], "hd8d1156bg4aebg47a5g8645gbb0afabb6083": ["*The dog watches the corpse, a quiet whine escaping with every breath.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "a57d0c39-0e99-4ca9-6cf7-c20109252641"], "had3f9efagc0e1g4a3bgab83gec491e48fb41": ["*Whine.*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "6a43fd6c-3e66-47e1-3eab-61dbc346ab34"], "h7b0480c3g5741g4576gb8a4gbd7efd37295c": ["*Arf! Arf! <i>Grrrrrarf!</i>*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "c2f925de-e0ef-a787-2cc6-444afe5df226"], "h248cc402g8b57g4814ga818g0676b8b68a59": ["<i>Reach out to pet him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "5f51a6a5-dd2e-467d-01a8-99c339d70b2e"], "h3485d18bg1df5g4a74g9acbgcf777e92e24c": ["*<i>Grrrr</i>-arf! Arf! Arf!*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "5e6a2cc2-ab06-d88c-511a-d92f9abcbfbe"], "h479192f6ga64fg4534g819cgb5a4cf6431df": ["It's all right, Scratch. I'm not going to hurt you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "5f484b06-9492-c423-9143-725a0705e5b1"], "h00e58c03gea20g44c6g88b2g6b3dde9dd698": ["<i>Kneel - you mean no harm.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "ef6ae581-ba3e-ac38-2c42-bceec36b62a9"], "h9d1f2951g1f8bg4eedga1b6g1e21032a12c7": ["*The dog lowers his hackles, his head titled inquisitively.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "d6fae196-a730-c7d8-6a54-e0b072663fa5"], "h3ccfb657gf4e1g42f8ga091gf747198a070c": ["*Convinced that you're harmless, he turns his attention back to the corpse.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "68922f04-9e19-140b-173b-1283bb34ecfd"], "h86cbd8a1g9191g4a93g8695gf6b44e0fa13d": ["You're okay, Scratch.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "4ede21df-0560-0b20-7754-acd9aa7d8aff"], "h2b0fa501g8d98g46dagb832g4bbed0951866": ["*With a deep, heartbroken whine, the dog bows his head.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "f164c6ce-64c7-9819-7c56-18534a515f24"], "he3f987afg47eeg405bgb7a2gf604db66bbc9": ["Come on, Scratch. Follow me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "91617a6c-b260-68ff-bc46-e163c64bfbc0"], "hd185ffb2geb55g4440gbe30gf6a94cc4d32d": ["*The dog looks at his owner with sad eyes. He does not move.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "f65a51de-7465-d643-1fe5-b75ba5b2c4b4"], "hd28f1ebegfc61g4782g8b66gad7f61ebb16c": ["*He whines, but remains rooted by the corpse's side.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "863f6d20-a79e-fcdb-055b-2338ab382bfe"], "hc78090dcgcf08g4e74gacf9gdd01f810137a": ["<i>Motion him to follow.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "1d5e351c-3ec9-bc42-23f3-bd95641f5e3b"], "ha3f89174gbfdcg40e8gac55gf172e8b28e73": ["<i>Hold out your hand so he can follow your scent to camp.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "d3a737ba-643d-5cc0-9837-d58c2ab82190"], "hced3a58eg4857g4956g8b3fgca93e7459363": ["*The dog sniffs your hand, his tail swung low in understanding. He knows how to find you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "da181859-57c1-d81c-574e-96a0d05a1bb4"], "h73aebfbdgc7e1g4234g8577g8950680476b0": ["*Sniff.*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "eb830180-9b8a-b083-9e02-f73d2a082e8a"], "h17613ef1g296eg41f4g8eecg1c1a6e35de0a": ["<i>Leave him to his sorrow.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "1d674fa8-06f3-7457-24ad-27abfd9778bd"], "h92e4f480gd817g4fbfg932dge6a6dd1fad21": ["<i>Take a closer look at him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "ba120469-db87-92c6-52c9-711b7c04c5cb"], "h37ca7558g72b3g40dfgbfd2g57c9da034723": ["*Around his neck is a collar, etched with a name - 'Scratch'.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "4d859cd7-3864-b359-e871-3ad32015cebf"], "h893c8baaga410g4294g8bd3ge7f73c08acce": ["<i>Shake your head - the man is gone.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "a5b5f6db-1321-0bb6-6493-2f3c7a33168a"], "hc487a536g341bg4108ga574gdcd689f57e77": ["<i>Pet him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "112b43da-f624-7203-9086-99aae4593c29"], "ha8d271b5g1387g4f9bga24fg01f620262a1f": ["*The dog whimpers nervously, as if to urge you on.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "3f163a2b-33b5-349f-3004-b1a6200070d0"], "hf336d7aagc05fg4116g859agacd187d8254b": ["*Whimper.*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "1827bbf8-899d-f82d-88c8-f1e58db950d8"], "h865884e5gfc94g41cfgbce4geea129b81a50": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "e7f55d4a-0ee6-f53f-ab54-4105a9dde2e2"], "hce373997g8faag4059g9d33g2dbeeb6da143": ["*The dog's hackles raise.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "8d00d86b-32fd-05ca-a394-483a64b9d575"], "h2fe6fe61g7bb9g4830ga7cfgc59ac639f0ae": ["<i>Peer at his collar.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "ee207b25-60f6-8a50-dbb3-7b824aaf3600"], "h780f6f2dgc9b9g49eegbb4eg582e2f5d14a5": ["*Grrrrafff!*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "9186c5b9-b3a8-c7a1-3607-532a74a8b755"], "h0aad8b94g1359g4f0bgaec6gfe6beab21f25": ["Stand down!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "62f8f3fd-5b78-b82a-834b-2cfa6030f776"], "h86ce70c4g3290g42b6ga80fg896ccaa02377": ["*Whine.*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "618cf4ac-6ff3-2b0d-1a1e-b95ec20f3259"], "h56ad4e7cg308eg45f8gaf45gf86cb4126a2b": ["*Arf! Arf!*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "0d59fa86-9fc9-4a7a-c441-4dc47cad836e"], "h53e03372g1bc3g4cecga312g6341acf13512": ["*Grrrrrr.*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "11f24384-c7f9-64d8-4d8e-1027f6b37a72"], "h5030addfg95eag4e44g927fg4fd4e626b1e0": ["<i>Growl deep in your throat.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "728645fe-c374-1151-3eda-e38241997b45"], "h9a4b1224gbf31g4467g820cgf16cf287e92c": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "2baa5596-79b8-467c-41b3-3b952aa7255b"], "h39c765e6g8e98g4fe2gad98g329cf9725d3a": ["<i>Sidestep him to get to the corpse.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "f2b4c128-69a1-1cfe-c1d1-8eebc2305431"], "h9e6eebbag96c4g4916gb51eg835483ae52f0": ["<i>Shoo him away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_Courier_Dog.html", "24b780a8-a740-4347-4124-b43e8a394bd2"]}